tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
  user_id UUID,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_visited VARCHAR,
  referrer VARCHAR,
  device_type VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE website_visitors (
    visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_name TEXT,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    visit_duration INTERVAL,
    visit_page TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE website_pages (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_title TEXT,
    page_url TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    campaign_start_date DATE,
    campaign_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE website_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_id INT REFERENCES website_pages(page_id),
    visits_count INT,
    bounce_rate FLOAT,
    average_time_on_page INTERVAL
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
  campaign_id INT,
  campaign_name VARCHAR,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  budget DECIMAL
);
